Overview: I created a basic home Soc from scratch. Using created a Azure subcription, opened up a new VM, opened that VM as a honeypot, and forward those logs to a central location. Finally using that info to build a map analyzing real world attacks.

Tools used:
1) Azure VM
2) Azure Setinel
3) Azure Analytics
4) Network Security Groups
5) Nmap

Skills learned:
KQL Language

